---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="Learn more about Yuna Colorsheets and our collection of printable coloring pages"
>
  <div class="about-container">
    <h1>About Yuna Colorsheets</h1>
    <p>
      Welcome to Yuna Colorsheets, your destination for high-quality printable coloring pages. 
      We specialize in creating unique and engaging coloring experiences for all ages, with a 
      special focus on Star Wars themed holiday coloring pages.
    </p>
    <p>
      Our coloring sheets are carefully designed to provide hours of creative enjoyment. Whether 
      you're a young Padawan or a Jedi Master, you'll find something special in our collection.
    </p>
    <h2>Why Choose Yuna Colorsheets?</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>High-quality, printable PDF format</li>
      <li>Unique and engaging designs</li>
      <li>Perfect for all skill levels</li>
      <li>Regular updates with new content</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-container {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  h1 {
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  h2 {
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
  }

  p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  ul {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>